No. 10-7791. Dewitt Gibson, Petitioner v. Dale Artis, Superintendent, Clinton Correctional Facility. 562 U.S. 1250, 131 S. Ct. 1483,

179 L. Ed. 2d 361,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1184. February 22, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 407 Fed. Appx. 517.
